{"word":"G3961 - πατέω - patéō - pat-eh'-o - Tread","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πατέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">patéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pat-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Tread</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மிதி, மிதிக்கப்படு"},{"paragraph":"to tread"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative probably of <a href=\"#/G3817 - παίω - paíō - pah'-yo/3817\">G3817</a> (meaning a &ldquo;path&rdquo;); to <i>trample</i> (literally or figuratively): - tread (down, under foot).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1704/1704\">G1704</a>, <a href=\"#/G2662/2662\">G2662</a>, <a href=\"#/G3961/3961\">G3961</a>, <a href=\"#/G4043/4043\">G4043</a>"}]}